{"title":"Esker Cycles Steel Smokey 160 mm Hardtail","link":"https://theradavist.com/esker-cycles-steel-smokey-160-mm-hardtail/","date":1721311798000,"content":"<p><img width=\"2384\" height=\"1589\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/Esker_Cycles_Smokey_Steel.jpg?fit=1200,1589&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/Esker_Cycles_Smokey_Steel.jpg?w=2384&amp;quality=75 2384w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/Esker_Cycles_Smokey_Steel.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/Esker_Cycles_Smokey_Steel.jpg?resize=2000,1333&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/Esker_Cycles_Smokey_Steel.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/Esker_Cycles_Smokey_Steel.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/Esker_Cycles_Smokey_Steel.jpg?resize=2048,1365&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p><em>Announced <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/esker-cycles-smokey-ti-hardtail/\" target=\"_blank\">last month</a> in a titanium chassis, the <a href=\"https://eskercycles.com/pages/smokey\" target=\"_blank\">Esker Cycles Smokey</a> is a 160 mm travel <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/?s=hardtail\" target=\"_blank\">hardtail</a> and now available in a steel frame. Let’s take a closer look…</em><span></span></p>\n<p><img width=\"1024\" height=\"682\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/DSC07882-Edit-Edit_1024x1024.jpg?resize=150,150&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/DSC07882-Edit-Edit_1024x1024.jpg?w=1024&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/DSC07882-Edit-Edit_1024x1024.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w\" /><img width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/DSC07944-Edit_1024x1024.jpg\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/DSC07944-Edit_1024x1024.jpg?w=1024&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/DSC07944-Edit_1024x1024.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/DSC07679-Edit-3_1024x1024.jpg?resize=150,150&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/DSC07679-Edit-3_1024x1024.jpg?w=1024&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/DSC07679-Edit-3_1024x1024.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w\" /></p>\n<p>Available as a <a href=\"https://eskercycles.com/products/2024-smokey-complete-bike\" target=\"_blank\">complete</a> ($3,000), a <a href=\"https://eskercycles.com/products/2024-smokey-frame\" target=\"_blank\">frame</a> ($1000), with the option to choose from a three fork models, the Smokey hits a nice pricepoint for those looking for a rowdier hardtail. We gotta say, the colors are really good, too!</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><strong>Esker Steel Smokey Quick Hits</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Optimized geometry for a 160mm suspension fork, steep seat tube angle, long reach and wheelbase.</li>\n<li>Accessory/tool mount under the top tube</li>\n<li>Custom drawn, seamless, double butted, heat treated 4130 DOM chromoly tube set.</li>\n<li>Tire Clearance: Fits a recommended tire size range from 2.4″ to 2.6″.</li>\n<li>Hydration ready: Accommodates 2 water bottles in the front triangle for MD, LG, and XL sizes.</li>\n<li>Adjustable UDH Portage Dropout to tune your perfect chainstay length or run as a singlespeed.</li>\n<li>Colors: Raven (Deep Metallic Grey), Lichen (Forest Service Green), Gold Bar (GOLD).</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2230\" height=\"1268\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/Screenshot-2024-07-18-at-8.00.03-AM.png?fit=1200,1268&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/Screenshot-2024-07-18-at-8.00.03-AM.png?w=2230&amp;quality=75 2230w, https://media.ther